Requirements
------------

* [sbt](https://github.com/harrah/xsbt/wiki) 0.10.1 (does not work/compile with sbt 0.10.0) or later. 


Installation
------------

**sbt 0.10.1:**

Add the following lines to ~/.sbt/plugins/build.sbt or PROJECT_DIR/project/plugins/build.sbt

    resolvers += "sbt-lab24-repo" at "http://lab24.github.com/maven/"
    
    libraryDependencies += "com.github.lab24" %% "sbt-mongodb" % "0.10.0"

**sbt 0.11.0:**

Add the following lines to ~/.sbt/plugins/build.sbt or PROJECT_DIR/project/plugins.sbt

    resolvers += "sbt-lab24-repo" at "http://mpeltonen.github.com/maven/"
    
    addSbtPlugin("com.github.lab24" % "sbt-mongodb" % "0.11.0")
    
**NOTE: If you experience problems with sbt 0.11 installation, [see this](https://github.com/mpeltonen/sbt-idea/issues/95).**

